---
Manage persisted REPL history

- Usage ----------------------------------------------------------------
  osp history [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>
------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Commands -------------------------------------------------------------
  list   List persisted history entries
  prune  Retain only the newest `keep` entries
  clear  Remove all persisted history entries
  help   Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Options --------------------------------------------------------------
  -i, --incognito                    Disable persistent REPL history and other identity-linked behavior
      --profile <PROFILE>            Select the active config profile for the invocation
      --no-env                       Skip environment-derived config sources
      --no-config-file               Skip config-file-derived sources
      --plugin-dir <PLUGIN_DIRS>     Add one or more plugin discovery directories
      --theme <THEME>                Override the selected output theme
      --presentation <PRESENTATION>  [possible values: expressive, compact, austere]
      --gammel-og-bitter
  -h, --help                         Print help
------------------------------------------------------------------------
